view_overrides.name: replace_product_variants_with_dropdown
view_overrides.replacement:
<%= t(:variants) %>
<% @product.option_types.sort_by { |ot| ot.position }.each do |option_type| %>
<%= label_tag option_type.presentation %>
<% end %>
<%= hidden_field_tag "products[#{@product.id}]", "", :id => 'product_id' %>

view_overrides.name: add_line_items_without_table
view_overrides.replacement:
<%= order_form.fields_for :line_items do |item_form| %> <% variant = item_form.object.variant line_item = item_form.object item_form = item_form %>
<% if variant.images.length == 0 %> <%= link_to small_image(variant.product), variant.product %> <% else %> <%= link_to image_tag(variant.images.first.attachment.url(:small)), variant.product %> <% end %>
<%= number_to_currency line_item.price %> <%= item_form.number_field :quantity, :min => 0, :class => "line_item_quantity", :size => 5 %> <%= link_to image_tag('icons/delete.png'), '#', :class => 'delete', :id => "delete_#{dom_id(line_item)}" %>

<%= link_to variant.product.name, product_path(variant.product) %>

<%= variant.options_text %> <% if @order.insufficient_stock_lines.include? line_item %> <%= variant.in_stock? ? t(:insufficient_stock, :on_hand => variant.on_hand) : t(:out_of_stock) %>
 <% end %> <%= truncate(variant.product.description, :length => 300, :omission => "...") %>
<% end %>
